{"id":"the-night-market-of-stars","slug":"the-night-market-of-stars","title":"The Night Market of Stars","title_ko":"별들의 밤 시장","level":"B1","ageBand":"11-13","coverUrl":"/seed/the-night-market-of-stars/cover.webp","summary_ko":"꿈속 별들의 밤 시장을 거닐며, 가장 소중한 것은 살 수 없고 나눌 때 얻는다는 걸 배우는 따뜻한 이야기.","wordCount":303,"pages":[{"id":"the-night-market-of-stars-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-night-market-of-stars/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-night-market-of-stars-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"One quiet night, Mina fell asleep while watching the sky.","translation_ko":"어느 고요한 밤, 미나는 하늘을 바라보다 잠이 들었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-night-market-of-stars/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"quiet","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":460,"endMs":880},{"word":"night","charStart":10,"charEnd":15,"startMs":880,"endMs":1240},{"word":"Mina","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":2000,"endMs":2060},{"word":"fell","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2340},{"word":"asleep","charStart":27,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2740},{"word":"while","charStart":34,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2740,"endMs":3160},{"word":"watching","charStart":40,"charEnd":48,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3400},{"word":"the","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3400,"endMs":3740},{"word":"sky","charStart":53,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3740,"endMs":3940}]},{"id":"the-night-market-of-stars-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"In her dream, a silver path opened high above the rooftops.","translation_ko":"꿈속에서 지붕들 위로 은빛 길이 활짝 열렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-night-market-of-stars/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"In","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":780},{"word":"her","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":780,"endMs":980},{"word":"dream","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":980,"endMs":1300},{"word":"a","charStart":14,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2120},{"word":"silver","charStart":16,"charEnd":22,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2360},{"word":"path",