night-market-of-stars-p10-s2","ord":1,"text":"Without thinking, Mina knelt down and gathered every glowing piece.","translation_ko":"미나는 망설임 없이 무릎을 꿇고 반짝이는 구슬을 하나하나 주워 모았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-night-market-of-stars/audio/p10-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Without","charStart":0,"charEnd":7,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"thinking","charStart":8,"charEnd":16,"startMs":380,"endMs":840},{"word":"Mina","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1480},{"word":"knelt","charStart":23,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1800},{"word":"down","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2200},{"word":"and","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2420},{"word":"gathered","charStart":38,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2660},{"word":"every","charStart":47,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2660,"endMs":3120},{"word":"glowing","charStart":53,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3120,"endMs":3380},{"word":"piece","charStart":61,"charEnd":66,"startMs":3380,"endMs":3840}]}]},{"id":"the-night-market-of-stars-p11","pageNo":11,"spread":"p11","imageUrl":"/seed/the-night-market-of-stars/p11.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-night-market-of-stars-p11-s1","ord":0,"text":"She handed the basket back and stayed to help until the stall was tidy again.","translation_ko":"바구니를 돌려준 뒤에도 가게가 다시 말끔해질 때까지 미나는 곁에서 도왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-night-market-of-stars/audio/p11-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"handed","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":300,"endMs":600},{"word":"the","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":600,"endMs":1080},{"word":"basket","charStart":15,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1080},{"word":"back","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1440},{"word":"and","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1780},{"word":"stayed","charStart":31,"charEnd":37,"startMs":1780,"endMs":1920},{"word":"to","charStart":38,"charEnd":40,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2220},{"word":"help","charStart":41,"charEnd":45,